name: "Climb The Life"
description:
Every problem, every pain, every risk, and every joy is the path of the mountain of life you just have to keep climbing. When you stop climbing you stop taking a risk, joy, adventure, excitement, fall, rise, faith, hope, emotion, feeling, and living. This artwork is made to shake off the people from their boring scheduled life to live once again with excitement and for what they love most in life. This artwork is inspired by mountainers' life. In "Climb the life" on one side we have a life of the modern world and one side natural world. The person climbing is the symbol of humankind where we all don't know where we have to reach but everyone is just climbing everyone's mountain of life. The colors shown in this artwork are more vibrant to portray the adventures and thrill of the world. 
Life is your so climb is yours "reach where you want"

"Climb The Life"
